name: Mallory Armstrong
text: Just placed an order for carry out and I want to say how polite one of the employees was! I believe his name is Cody but every time we order he is very nice, attentive and easy to talk too. We’ve also had pleasant experiences every time we order carry out and choose this Pizza Hut over other places in the area.

name: Melody Dhooghe
text: Called at 4 min until 4pm , (their opening time) and attempted to place an order to pick up through the drive thru.  I was told they were not open yet and could not take my order. Seriously Pizza Hut? Is your business flourishing so much in …More

name: Michael Myers
text: Dear owner operator manager. Your store was our choice tonight, and I will not make that mistake again. Food is cold and your manager Becky is beyond rude. We ordered 80.00 in pizza and wings and got no sauces. I questioned your manager and got a rude belligerent woman. I will now be going to Columbus from here on out. Thank you.

name: Bob Thomas
text: Nice place but the tables needed to be wiped off and salt and pepper shakers needs to be wiped off to. Very sticky and the top fell off the red pepper shaker and everything thing fell out on my pizza. And it was around 3:30 pm. No one else in there so I think they could have been cleaning up for the supper time.

text: Pizza awful. dried out. Italian sausage look like black olives. Salty tasting Won't go back

name: Rachel Duncan
text: I was with my friends.   We each got the lunch special.  All you can eat.    It was very delicious.   They had pizza, salad, cottage cheese, and beets.   I love beets.  They had other salad stuff too.  It was awesome.
